{
  "id": "6a0193eed3ef27b9b176f2b6",
  "title": "僕が井戸端に居続ける意味は何だろう",
  "created": 1778488302,
  "updated": 1778488307,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a0193eed3ef27b9b176f2b6",
      "text": "僕が井戸端に居続ける意味は何だろう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778488302,
      "updated": 1778488302
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0193ee00000000000bccf8",
      "text": "from [2025/03/08]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778488302,
      "updated": 1778488302
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0193ee00000000000bccf9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778488302,
      "updated": 1778488307
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0193ee00000000000bccfa",
      "text": "[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778488302,
      "updated": 1778488302
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0193ee00000000000bccfb",
      "text": " 僕が井戸端に居続ける意味は何だろう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778488302,
      "updated": 1778488302
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0193ee00000000000bccfc",
      "text": "　別に個人プロジェクトに引き篭もるのでもいい気がした",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778488302,
      "updated": 1778488302
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0193ee00000000000bccfd",
      "text": "　利点",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778488302,
      "updated": 1778488302
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0193ee00000000000bccfe",
      "text": "　　他の人からコメントを貰える",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778488302,
      "updated": 1778488302
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0193ee00000000000bccff",
      "text": "　　今までと同じ場所に日記を書ける",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778488302,
      "updated": 1778488302
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0193ee00000000000bcd00",
      "text": "　　ついでに他の人の日記も読み漁れる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778488302,
      "updated": 1778488302
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0193ee00000000000bcd01",
      "text": "　欠点",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778488302,
      "updated": 1778488302
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0193ee00000000000bcd02",
      "text": "　　他の人からコメントが来る",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778488302,
      "updated": 1778488302
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0193ee00000000000bcd03",
      "text": "　　いろんな人の書き込みがあるので重い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778488302,
      "updated": 1778488302
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0193ee00000000000bcd04",
      "text": "　　自分の目の前にあるもの以外が目に入る",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778488302,
      "updated": 1778488302
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0193ee00000000000bcd05",
      "text": "　　　他人の投稿を見るフェーズと自分の書き込みをするフェーズは分けた方が良いかもしれない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778488302,
      "updated": 1778488302
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0193ee00000000000bcd06",
      "text": "　[井戸端離れ]して個人プロジェクトに引き篭もるか？",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778488302,
      "updated": 1778488302
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0193ee00000000000bcd07",
      "text": "　　他人に[研磨]されないと[エゴ]が強くなりそうだけど、それは他人に要求することではない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778488302,
      "updated": 1778488302
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0193ee00000000000bcd08",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778488302,
      "updated": 1778488302
    }
  ]
}